description.narrative: Output 8.2: By 2019, evidence based and equity-focused programme planning, monitoring and evaluation institutionalized., which contributes to Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses, Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Fostering Innovation And Use Of New Technologies, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Outcome 8: By 2019, National and sub-national capacity on evidence based planning, and management enhanced to emphasis on children and women's disparities across sectors.
